Board.recipe.hooks.prebuild.2.pattern: cmd /c if not exist "{build.path}\partitions.csv" if exist "{build.variant.path}\partitions.csv" COPY "{build.variant.path}\partitions.csv" "{build.path}\partitions.csv"

Board.recipe.hooks.prebuild.4.pattern: cmd /c IF EXIST "{build.source.path}\bootloader.bin" ( COPY /y "{build.source.path}\bootloader.bin" "{build.path}\{build.project_name}.bootloader.bin" ) ELSE ( IF EXIST "{build.variant.path}\bootloader.bin" ( COPY "{build.variant.path}\bootloader.bin" "{build.path}\{build.project_name}.bootloader.bin" ) ELSE ( COPY /y "{runtime.platform.path}\tools\sdk\{build.mcu}\bin\bootloader_{build.boot}_{build.flash_freq}.bin" "{build.path}\{build.project_name}.bootloader.bin" ) )
Board.recipe.hooks.prebuild.4.pattern.windows: cmd /c IF EXIST "{build.source.path}\bootloader.bin" ( COPY /y "{build.source.path}\bootloader.bin" "{build.path}\{build.project_name}.bootloader.bin" ) ELSE ( IF EXIST "{build.variant.path}\bootloader.bin" ( COPY "{build.variant.path}\bootloader.bin" "{build.path}\{build.project_name}.bootloader.bin" ) ELSE ( COPY /y "{runtime.platform.path}\tools\sdk\{build.mcu}\bin\bootloader_{build.boot}_{build.flash_freq}.bin" "{build.path}\{build.project_name}.bootloader.bin" ) )
